description: Khalid al-Saleh moves to Germany with his family, having fled Syrian government forces.
title: Germany takes in Syrian White Helmets ex-leader
title_page: Germany takes in Syrian White Helmets ex-leader - BBC News
maintext: There was also reportedly pressure from the Jordanian authorities, who had agreed to let the Syrians stay for three months on condition that they then moved to Germany, the UK or Canada. Those nations had agreed to take them in, Jordan said.
